'''Ainea Ojiambo''' (yavutse 20 Mata 1970), ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Kenya]]. <ref>https://elcinema.com/en/person/2066570/</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime ''[[The Constant Gardener (film)|The Constant Gardener]]'', ''[[Bullion (film)|Bullion]]'' na ''Jack Zollo: My life in crime''. <ref>https://www.kenyans.co.ke/news/51217-love-gold-led-kenyan-actor-scammers-video</ref> <ref>http://www.filmstarts.de/personen/516924.html</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 20 Mata 1970 i [[Nairobi]], muri [[Kenya]] . Ni se w'abana babiri, umuhungu n'umukobwa.

== Umwuga ==
Mbere yo kwinjira muri ecran ikunzwe, yakoraga mumikino myinshi kandi nuburyo umwuga we wo gukina watangiye. <ref>https://coursediscovery.com/biography-of-ainea-ojiambo-net-worth-2021biography-of-ainea-ojiambo-net-worth-2021/</ref> Mu 2004, yatumiriwe gukina muri firime ya Hollywood ''[[The Constant Gardener (film)|The Constant Gardener]]'' iyobowe na Fernando Meirelles . <ref name="sqoop">https://www.sqoop.co.ug/201404/features/one-on-one-with-kenyan-bullion-actor-ainea-ojiambo.html</ref> Muri filime, yakinnye uruhare ruto rwa 'Umushoferi wa Polisi'. Filime yagenze neza kandi yinjiza amafaranga menshi kandi yegukana ibihembo bine bya Oscar . Hanyuma mu 2007, yakinnye muri tereviziyo ya [[Kenya]] ''Makutano Junction'' afite uruhare mu 'nzoka'. <ref>http://www.makutanojunction.org.uk/the-soap/the-characters/snake.html?phpMyAdmin=1fsBD3w5EHXJC4U4sqKUm1Rz7kc</ref>

Nyuma yo gutsinda k'uruhererekane, nyuma yaje gutumirwa gukina izindi televiziyo ebyiri: ''Block-D'' na ''Noose ya Zahabu'' . Muri opera yisabune ''Noose ya Zahabu'', Ojiambo yakinnye nka 'Ole Mpisha'. <ref>http://wapend.com/video/Ole_Mpisha_and_breakfast_Noose_of_Gold/zrV_10ncp6k</ref> Isabune yaje gutangazwa ibihe 3 muri [[Afurika|Afrika]] muri Afrika Magic Channel . Mu mwaka wa 2010, yakoze filime ye ya kabiri ya Hollywood ''[[The First Grader]]'', filime yerekana ikinamico yayobowe na Justin Chadwick . Muri filime, yagize uruhare runini nka 'Ushinzwe uburezi'. <ref name="sqoop" />

Mu myaka yakurikiyeho, yagaragaye muri firime muri firime, ''The Rugged Padiri'', ''[[Fundi-Mentals]]'', ''[[Nairobi Half Life]]'', ''Gukurikira Yesu'', ''Babuz Babies'', ''Kibera Kid'', ''Amaboko'' ''afunze'', ''Stigma'', Obohoz, ''Padiri Rugged'', ''Guerilla Boy'', na ''LoveDoctor'' . <ref>http://kenya.spla.pro/en/file.person.ainea-ojiambo.43134.html</ref> Mu mwaka wa 2014, yagaragaye muri filime yâ€™ikinamico yo [[Ubugande|muri Uganda]] ''[[Bullion (film)|Bullion]] yatowe'' <ref>https://whownskenya.com/index.php/2021/04/30/ainea-ojiambo-biography-age-career-con-story-and-shooting/,%20https://whownskenya.com/index.php/2021/04/30/ainea-ojiambo-biography-age-career-con-story-and-shooting/</ref> ''muri Oscars'' afite uruhare runini. <ref>https://www.ugandanewsreleases.com/%EF%BB%BFbullion-premieres-saturday/</ref>

